Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I'm him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He reminded me of you during the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He would have gotten an advantage if he played\Nin the corner instead of connecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Black's winning by a little this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:10.70,Sai,,0,0,0,,Everyone around us is starting\Nto notice Hikaru's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:12.95,Sai,,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:16.49,Sai,,0,0,0,,The brilliant future that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:19.49,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru has, shining above him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:21.08,Sai,,0,0,0,,The future I lack...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:27.09,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(330,115)}The Fifty-Eighth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:27.09,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}One-Color Go
