Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:43.98,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\fs19\fscx99\fad(542,542)\shad0\bord3\pos(320,364)}Kurata Atsushi 6-Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:48.48,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\fs19\fscx99\fad(501,501)\shad0\bord3\pos(320,364)}Kamaishi Yoshirou 9-Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:46.66,Background,,0,0,0,,Kurata-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from the smile, I'm guessing you won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to blast through this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seriously aiming for a title now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:04:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess even Kamaishi 9-dan is no\Nmatch for Kurata-kun anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Over in Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The fifth game of the Jyudan match?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you stopped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:15.28,Background,,0,0,0,,Let's see, the fax did arrive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:17.03,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the latest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from half an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:25.87,Background,,0,0,0,,The game's still pretty even, after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:30.17,Background,,0,0,0,,So I think Master Touya's going to end up\Nwinning, since he is more experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:39.93,Background,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ogata just isn't as good as Master\NTouya with the finishing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He was defeated in the seventh and\Nfinal game of the Honinbou match,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and he may lose today in the fifth and\Nfinal game of the Jyudan match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll toughen up once\Nhe gets used to title matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,His game is starting to get solid and professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, what's\Nwrong with Touya Kouyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ogata-san is playing it rationally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? The Meijin is still playing moves like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unlike him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Touya... lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.41,Sai,,0,0,0,,He lost?
