Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:55.13,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fad(0,1460)\1c&H000000&\3c&HBBBEBB&\bord6\shad0\fscx98\fscy130\b0\frz311\i1\pos(220.426,274.269)}and Touya Kouyou now has{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:55.13,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs12\fad(0,1460)\1c&H000000&\3c&HBBBEBB&\bord6\shad0\fscx98\fscy130\b0\frz311\i1\pos(194.926,273.269)}four titles left to defend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,With formulas like these, what\Nyou want to be solving for is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.63,Background,,0,0,0,,Listen up, this part is going to be on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:07.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why did Master Touya lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Was it because he played Go against Sai on the Internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:17.62,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he lost because he was tired\Nfrom it, or if it threw him off rhythm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:20.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I hope that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.66,Sai,,0,0,0,,I doubt that would be the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.62,Sai,,0,0,0,,But I would have to look at the Kifu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kifu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.20,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:37.41,Sai,,0,0,0,,I can tell what he felt during the\Nmatch if I look at the Kifu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:40.38,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you're finally back to normal, Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've been acting strangely lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked really sad all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not Touya, but you looked just\Nas inconfident and worried as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.45,Sai,,0,0,0,,N-No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.04,Sai,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Master Touya is really going to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:20.67,Sai,,0,0,0,,He's not the type of person who changes his\Nmind after he's decided on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.09,Sai,,0,0,0,,He isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.64,Background,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:34.48,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\blur0.6\shad0\bord0\frz90\fscy120\1c&H4231AB&\pos(65,281)}RAMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:34.48,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs14.5\blur0.6\shad0\bord0\frz90\fscy160\1c&H4231AB&\pos(90,281)}Yamanishi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to look at the Kifu, but I'm not sure\Nif I can get it at the Institute or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Weekly Go won't come out until next week...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:45.19,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fax-0.18\fry-18\frx4\fs27.5\shad0\bord0\fscy120\fscx102\1c&HB2DCF1&\frz22.16\pos(249,187)}RAMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.80,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.24,Background,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.08,Background,,0,0,0,,Kurata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot? Shindou, are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hear to eat noodles of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking why you're in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to treat you just\Nbecause you sat down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can pay for it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You, too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Two Ramens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have an appointment for\Na tutoring game around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Kurata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see the Kifu from the Jyudan game\Nyesterday if I go to the Go Institute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You did!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was at the Go Institute yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So the publishing division showed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They send you updates on the\Ngame live over the fax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Master Touya lost... I\Nread about it in the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What... kind of a game was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A game you wouldn't expect from Touya Kouyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't expect!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think he plays a well-balanced game?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He attacks when he should but\Nholds back when he needs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if he was off balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it... poorly played?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a great game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He played interesting moves one after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,even though it was the last game of a title match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,His game has become more youthful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He ended up losing, but I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he can still change\Nhis game despite his age!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Kouyou is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still at his prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my impression of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to eat, Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:10.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So it was a good game...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.18,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Then he might not retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.67,Background,,0,0,0,,That makes defeating him all the more\Nworthy a goal. I'm getting excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:19.72,Background,,0,0,0,,His son put up a great fight, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurata-san, you've played Touya Akira before!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I beat him last month in the second\Npreliminaries for the Meijin match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's made it to the third preliminaries\Nfor the Honinbou match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A mere 2-dan is in the third preliminaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no rivals amongst the lower dan players.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.87,Background,,0,0,0,,He might really become threatening by summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.83,Background,,0,0,0,,It's faster than I could've imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:45.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:48.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So you've already made it that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:53.05,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Can I not even catch up to him? Let alone surpass him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.01,Background,,0,0,0,,Thank you, come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a great meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you busy right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please play a game against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What'll I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:31.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's bitter about my saying\Nthat I didn't want his autograph...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:39.10,Background,,0,0,0,,I want Kurata-san's autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurata-san, will you give me your autograph\Nas a reward if I beat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:45.06,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(647,485)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:45.10,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(611,464)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:45.14,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(584,450)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:45.18,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(553,432)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:45.23,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(525,417)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:45.27,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(500,402)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:45.31,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(479,390)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:45.35,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(462,380)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:45.39,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(451,375)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.02,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fad(0,584)\frz316\pos(447,372)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:49.69,Background,,0,0,0,,Well, I doubt someone like me could win,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't ask for Kurata-san's autograph for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something I have to work hard for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Reeeaally?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You want it that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go to a Go salon somewhere then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Score!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really easy to manipulate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:19.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:24.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,We'll test my strength out, by seeing how\Nwell I can play against Kurata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:31.69,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HF9ECE5&\alpha&H80&\fs55\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscx155\fscy90\move(280,272,82,272)}GO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:31.69,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HF9ECE5&\alpha&H80&\fs18.5\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscx100\fscy70\move(570,298,372,298)}Beginners
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:31.69,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HF9ECE5&\alpha&H80&\fs20.5\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscx100\fscy70\move(569,310,371,310)}Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.94,Background,,0,0,0,,You pay the entrance fee, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.22,Background,,0,0,0,,For both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:31.69,Background,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.32,Background,,0,0,0,,K-Kurata the pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurata!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's Kurata! Kurata 6-dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is him! I'm a fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we play?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course! This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurata-san! We'll be cheering you on\Nfor the Honinbou match next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all just talking about how Kurata-san's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Honinbou title will follow Ogata-san's Jyudan title.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kurata, who is your companion here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Him? His name is Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He just became a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:10.06,Background,,0,0,0,,He asked me to give him my\Nautograph if he beats me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:13.23,Background,,0,0,0,,So he's Kurata-san's fan! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have your autograph later as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we have any autograph paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An even match is too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so Shindou you can play first with no Komi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I won't give you my autograph for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:29.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.42,Background,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:32.95,Background,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.25,Background,,0,0,0,,They're both white.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are some Black stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, let's play like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:42.30,Background,,0,0,0,,One-Color Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One-Color Go!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's played with White\Nor Black, just one color.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou, yours is Black, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!? These white stones are black?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, say 'good luck'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:02.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This stone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Black!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:08.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Looks like this is Shindou's first\Ntime playing One-Color Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:12.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's just starting to get interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing with just white stones?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If all of the stones in this game we're playing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:23.01,Background,,0,0,0,,are replaced by white stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they can both play with only white.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the kid white or black?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:53.33,Background,,0,0,0,,He's black!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep quiet, I'm going to lose track here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:06.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:17.31,Background,,0,0,0,,I can still kind of keep track...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.45,Background,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see more than you\Nthought you could, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember it by the shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The shape of the stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shape, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:42.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Didn't he teach Mr. Gokiso a lesson\Nduring that convention?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shape? But to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost track.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped focusing for a second, and I've lost track.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've still got a ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.31,Background,,0,0,0,,Right, Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:06.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gokiso isn't a match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow Muranishi-san, you still\Nknow what's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost track a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:15.46,Background,,0,0,0,,It's just determination now. I'm\Ndetermined to keep track of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, someone can still see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to ditch you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:24.83,Background,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A furious battle's started in the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...or that's what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we have no idea what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:43.82,Background,,0,0,0,,It just looks like this clump of white stones\Nthat keeps getting bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We've still got a ways to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Who's winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.37,Background,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.17,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Who's winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Umm... Mr. Kurata...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's winning right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's working very hard to stay ahead right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He must really want my autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He won't give me a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I misread it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:38.54,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou just made a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,... I'm saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:49.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm not playing Touya Kouyou or\Nold man Kuwabara right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:53.63,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's a kid that just became pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:17:59.81,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Wait! Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou's first time playing One-Color Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It isn't just Touya Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:11.29,Thinking,,0,0,0,,who's going to be threatening me from below...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There's another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:27.67,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Crap! I lost track of the stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.63,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Around there... it's around there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:36.09,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Umm... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:40.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Will Black die if I move here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally misread this part.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was complicated, but I'm sure I could have won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:13.92,Background,,0,0,0,,I totally messed up by making a ko here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have moved cautiously here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have replied on the right side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:21.63,Background,,0,0,0,,Right? Kurata-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.45,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:27.00,Sai,,0,0,0,,He has realized it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:29.85,Sai,,0,0,0,,He's seen Hikaru's hidden strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have autograph paper? Extra ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh! Of course, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Weren't you going to give him\Nan autograph only if he won?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:47.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I don't want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.59,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs42\1c&H0B0909&\shad0\bord0\blur0.8\frz4\pos(364,259)\b1}Kura{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.38,Background,,0,0,0,,It's just 'Kura'?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sign the rest of it when you\Nbeat me in a formal match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kurata, may I have an autograph as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,One for me, too, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.81,Background,,0,0,0,,Line up if you want one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:11.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Kurata-san's... recognized me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:16.99,Background,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.53,Background,,0,0,0,,Turn the volume up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(834,0)}In an earlier press conference, the top Go player,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Kouyou, with four titles,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,has announced his retirement!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya's...
