Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai-chan, have you heard of Seki before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:22.93,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(417,501)\3c&H018A0A&\4c&H018A0A&\fscx99\fscy90\bord1.5\shad0.5\pos(320,356)}Seki... when neither side can capture the other
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Seki is a situation when you are both close to capturing,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but can't capture the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.59,0:22:25.55,Background,,0,0,0,,Don't both White and Black have a shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:28.53,Background,,0,0,0,,where they're close to capturing\Nand close to getting captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:30.30,Background,,0,0,0,,If it's Black's turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.17,0:22:29.42,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(250,0)\3c&HDA00D0&\4c&HDA00D0&\fscx99\fscy90\bord1.5\shad0.5\move(600,40,189,40)}If {\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}Black {\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HDA00D0&\4c&HDA00D0&}goes to capture
