Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.17,0:22:29.42,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(250,0)\3c&H0769E3&\4c&H0769E3&\fscx99\fscy90\bord1.5\shad0.5\move(750,355,320,355)}If you try to capture, you get captured instead{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:36.27,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,501)\3c&H0769E3&\4c&H0769E3&\fscx99\fscy90\bord1.5\shad0.5\pos(320,355)}If you try to capture, you get captured instead{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:32.54,Background,,0,0,0,,and Black plays here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:36.37,Background,,0,0,0,,White plays here, and five stones get captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:38.48,Background,,0,0,0,,It's the same with White.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:36.82,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(250,0)\3c&H0769E3&\4c&H0769E3&\fscx99\fscy90\bord1.5\shad0.5\move(760,355,320,355)}If you try to capture, you get captured instead{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:40.61,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,0)\3c&H0769E3&\4c&H0769E3&\fscx99\fscy90\bord1.5\shad0.5\pos(320,355)}If you try to capture, you get captured instead{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:43.85,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,0)\3c&H0769E3&\4c&H0769E3&\fscx99\fscy90\bord1.5\shad0.5\pos(320,355)}You won't get captured, if you don't try to capture{\i1}!{\i0}
